snippet.title: The Binding of Isaac: Rebirth Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
PRE-ORDER NOW! http://store.steampowered.com/app/250900

IT'S HAPPENING! The Binding of Isaac: Rebirth coming to PlayStation 4, PS Vita and Steam!  

The Binding of Isaac: Rebirth is more items, more enemies, more bosses, local co-op, all-new art direction and a killer new soundtrack that will BLOW YOUR MIND. 

Limited-time loyalty discount for owners of the original!

http://www.bindingofisaac.com
http://www.nicalis.com

And don't forget to tell your mom...

Video directed and produced by @jamesid
